{"tid":437772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法媒稱「強國崛起」中國直呼這是中國發展現狀 驚覺被反酸、急下架新聞","createTime":"2017-10-16T09:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T05:29:04.000Z","uid":37554,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"66960cc2dfd4ed79d67a6cf9de66d2fbca3c5d75","tid":437772,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpihHlwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpihHlwu.jpg&h=cf0e6db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國第二大全國性日報《世界報》，於昨日星期天的頭版，放上號外專刊，在全法文的報紙上，斗大寫著中文「中國，強國崛起」。中國官媒《環球時報》、《央視》見狀，喜孜孜地直呼這就是中國迅速發展的現狀。但這篇文章其實諷刺許多中國內政，《央視》發現後嚇得趕快刪除新聞，但網頁的頁庫存檔仍看得到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpK8hCrR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpK8hCrR.jpg&h=a1b93089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/540/https://holland.pk/vwr3qa4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvwr3qa4d&h=6a37efce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《世界報》專刊消息傳到微博後，引起不少中國網友熱血沸騰，直呼中國終於被全世界看到了，各大媒體也發文盛讚。但看得懂法文的中國人還是存在的，因此發現事情不單純，也開始在微博發出質疑的聲浪，導致原本在《央視》上報導的影片已被移除。然而微博上批評中國官媒弄錯法媒意思的文章，也莫名一個接一個地「被消失」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnkYg0X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnkYg0X.jpg&h=8afb40ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《法廣》報導，《世界報》原文的內容，關注在中共19大議題上，陳述習近平如何控制內政與經濟，藉此與美國抗衡。文章裡強調，習近平掌權後，加強對社會的管制，並且對企業集團下手，以便將其納入管理。更有甚者，中國政府還嚴管網路，讓網路世界陷入冰河階段。<br />\n<br />\n《法廣》指出，《世界報》文章闡述習近平在「奪取政權」後，為了鞏固統治，才在軍方和民間大力打擊貪污。此外，中國開放派律師與記者，同樣受到嚴厲打壓，被政府緊密監控。因此，習近平對於中國內政，無疑使用了高壓統治手段。"},{"pid":"e5ad52a9e684cec45fbefb49932d6ad2df636fc9","tid":437772,"uid":37554,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/bb229ae1cb754dcee1b99128b8b292e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fbb229ae1cb754dcee1b99128b8b292e7.png&h=68ff64ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13c7002a809c6bb381d913c71b4880e68e71337a","tid":437772,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7511106eee099571f32e8065fa74d92c747506ab","tid":437772,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7742f82038b66a8a2f306d7098635892ac84d49e","tid":437772,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667fc81b7c23fe628682f598f6c705088a65875b","tid":437772,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534c314e5d42cef90916af9f0b593f06f2f3e20c","tid":437772,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:55:45.000Z","msg":"識法文既中國人，真係幾勁"},{"pid":"908ec517b8d972d4aad4c941edc363d6cf94f67b","tid":437772,"uid":3028,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/65510_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWha